title: Green Cup Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Organic, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe est. 2014 at originally at 2200 First St as all-vegetarian; moved here in 2016 and added fish and chicken. On the menu are coffee and loose leaf tea, juices and smoothies, bowls, salads, and wraps. Has vegan ice cream and raw dessert. Gluten-free options. Vegan milk and cheese substitutes available.
